headline: Defense Contractors Stocks Q3 In Review: Leidos (NYSE:LDOS) Vs Peers
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Leidos (NYSE:LDOS) and the rest of the defense contractors stocks fared in Q3.
